    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition and presents as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior paint is flawless, with a deep, mirror-like finish and no stone chips, scratches, or imperfections of any kind. Inside, the cabin is pristine, with the leather upholstery still smelling new and every electronic feature functioning perfectly. Mechanically, the car is sound, having been meticulously maintained with a full service history and very low mileage. You will not find a better-preserved example on the market today.",
