      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is currently best suited as a project car or for parts. The engine struggles to stay idle and exhibits a persistent knocking sound, while the transmission slips significantly between gears. Visually, the body has several large dents, noticeable rust on the wheel arches, and the interior upholstery is heavily worn and torn. It will require a comprehensive mechanical overhaul and bodywork to be safely returned to the road.",
