      "description": "This meticulously maintained vehicle represents a premier opportunity for the discerning driver. Characterized by its robust mechanical integrity and refined presentation, it offers a sophisticated driving experience that exceeds standard expectations for its class. Every component has been thoroughly vetted to ensure continued performance and safety. We invite you to experience the caliber of this exceptional offering firsthand.",
      "price": 34800.0,
